        <title type="html"><![CDATA[25/3/15 抽滤，等待下午消逝。]]></title>
        <id>https://EfeiSongs.github.io/post/waterlab1/</id>
        <link href="https://EfeiSongs.github.io/post/waterlab1/">
        </link>
        <updated>2025-03-15T06:25:00.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>换滤膜，开关真空泵，转移滤液。<br>
<img src="https://EfeiSongs.github.io/post-images/1742020715555.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://EfeiSongs.github.io/post-images/1742020722370.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
晚餐：沙县小吃，杂酱面+煎蛋，小笼包。共21元。</p>
<p>%作者：slandarer<br>
%链接：https://www.zhihu.com/question/27780598/answer/758261793<br>
bkgPic=imread('5e0f4c5b6edce3b8d8d26710d026b9a.jpg');%图片地址<br>
% lineDensity故障线条密度 | lineLenRange故障线条长度范围 | greenMoveLen绿移距离<br>
[m,n,k]=size(bkgPic);lineDensity=0.6;lineLenRange=[50,80];greenMoveLen=10;<br>
if k~=1,bkgPic=rgb2gray(bkgPic);end<br>
colorList=[21,27,143;68,22,113;94,72,151;175,152,192;221,188,204;217,156,174;203,82,104;232,31,37;151,5,11]';<br>
blueRedPic=cat(3,repmat(interp1(linspace(1,n,size(colorList,2)),colorList(1,:),1:n,'linear'),[m,1]),repmat(interp1(linspace(1,n,size(colorList,2)),colorList(2,:),1:n,'linear'),[m,1]),repmat(interp1(linspace(1,n,size(colorList,2)),colorList(3,:),1:n,'linear'),[m,1]));<br>
blueRedPic=uint8(double(blueRedPic).<em>double(bkgPic)./200);<br>
gm_brPic=cat(3,blueRedPic(:,1+greenMoveLen:end,1),blueRedPic(:,1:end-greenMoveLen,2),blueRedPic(:,1+greenMoveLen:end,3));<br>
[~,movePos]=sort(rand(1,m));movePos=sort(movePos(1:floor(m</em>lineDensity)));movePic=gm_brPic(movePos,:,1);<br>
for i=1:size(movePic,1),gm_brPic(movePos(i),:,1)=imfilter(movePic(i,:),fspecial('motion',randi(lineLenRange,[1,1]),0),'replicate');end<br>
imshow(gm_brPic);</p>
]]></content>
